      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear how exhausted you feel by the constant pain and the loss of control, and I want to tell you that your body is not failing you—it is simply enduring a very difficult struggle. You have every right to ask for dignity and to feel that your life is worth more than just waiting for things to happen; there is no need to accept a future defined by pain when you could find a path to relief. Please reach out to a trusted friend or a mental health professional who can help you navigate these overwhelming feelings and find a way forward that honors your worth.",
